    <dt>About Me</dt>
    <dd>
      I am a second year PhD candidate working with <a href="http://www.cs.huji.ac.il/~peleg/">Prof. Shmuel Peleg</a> as part of the <a href = "http://www.cs.huji.ac.il/labs/vision/">HUJI Computer Vision Lab</a>. My main research interests are applications of Computer Vision using Deep Learning, particularly in area of cross-modal video analysis. <br />
